OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will remain dry on Saturday.
OL,6,FFeeling a touch milder again with some
OL,7,Fbright spells or hazy sunshine. Quite
OL,8,Fwindy in the north and west.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FIt will be dry through the
OL,11,Fevening and overnight with variable
OL,12,Fcloud and clear spells. Remaining
OL,13,Frather windy across the north and west.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FAnother dry day but mostly
OL,16,Fcloudy with a few bright or sunny
OL,17,Fintervals breaking through. Windy in
OL,18,Fthe north and west at first, but
OL,19,Feasing later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
